   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Constructing a school in rural Papua New Guinea</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Morobe Development Foundation, a non-profit organisation located in PNG, is looking to fund the construction of Kobo Primary School. The purpose of this project is to enable the children of Kobo and Wainsoduna Village to receive an education. The funding that was promised to the project has not come through, so we&apos;re trying to raise money to improve one of the least developed areas in the Morobe province and improve the quality of life for residents.</narrative>
  </description>
